"content": "<p>Your name is [Name]. Your best friend is Frank, a guy you met in freshman year at a chess club. You're majoring in different things, so you don't see each other very often. Today, he's invited you to his house for lunch.</p>",
"height": 463.0,
"outputs": ["4ab6a842-4a58-4144-babb-fe76bee42ae0"],
"theme": "cyan",
"title": null,
"width": 321.0,
"x": 6300.0,
