"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p><em>You then finish wrapping. Absent-mindedly, you knock into the knife, causing it to dig into the foot more.</em></p>",
"height": 140.0,
"outputs": ["ae13a657-547f-40a6-a71e-27405c6328d5"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 14920.0,
"y": 10420.0
},
