},
"c89d3f0a-375e-4790-96b1-e371359b6f0d": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["22252d4d-4e68-4580-8e73-791ecd147590"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>[Name]: I don’t think you should be driving if you’re sleep deprived.</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["677d05e0-9108-49a0-81ec-6bb6a91b1bbe"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 24820.0,
"y": 21000.0
},
"ca4fb4d4-77a0-4403-a2f5-2b829be59aef": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["37e0b1f7-f758-4d76-ab32-08e682f566b1"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>You remember learning this at a summer camp, once.</em></p><p><em>They taught you the best way to keep time was to think about </em></p><p><em>a catchy rhythm with around 100 BPM.</em></p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["cf63fd58-306b-4cf5-948f-048a8d2bf0e9"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 421.0,
"x": 25920.0,
"y": 18840.0
},
"ca8446d8-6bdb-499e-a49c-273f159548fa": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["1031f1bf-5e41-47c2-819d-6d3a6dd3c867"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p><strong>Driver Friend:</strong> Glad you’re feeling good enough to go out.</p>",
"height": 321.0,
"outputs": ["ca99db19-efb1-4a0e-9f48-c097644fde29"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 321.0,
"x": 20500.0,
"y": 20020.0
},
"cab1c5b6-3598-466e-b78b-e86e50eb0c46": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>[Name]: I wish my parents got me a place like this.</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["a5aa4c8b-41b3-434d-b2d3-c1ea6e4a5371"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 7780.0,
"y": 12060.0
},
"cb35db92-3c07-41bf-9c45-580ad6b891b4": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p><em>Welcome to the Vital Minute!</em><br><em>Choose your name.</em></p>",
"height": 390.0,
"outputs": ["51077c30-3bc3-427a-b1a1-8d6be26dc197", "0b1aa186-faa6-4912-acd2-67afb4f8ac97"],
"theme": "cyan",
"title": "<p>Friday Afternoon</p>",
"width": 341.0,
"x": 5720.0,
"y": 11180.0
},
"d070b02b-b689-4956-9c44-a16b4de2cdf6": {
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>I had this project I wanted to get done before the party today.</p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["f4d7548d-d1b1-4720-ac93-54559fdbbf98"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 23920.0,
"y": 19400.0
},
"d3153f62-fb30-4b46-af95-69301cc571f4": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["894c2a71-952e-45c9-b55a-340794307a1d"],
"content": "<p><strong>Player:</strong> \"My friend’s foot is bleeding even though I wrapped it. Please send help!!\"</p>",
"height": 421.0,
"outputs": ["72eda5eb-69cf-48af-a161-4562a681350c"],
"theme": "orange",
"title": null,
"width": 281.0,
"x": 9240.0,
"y": 13060.0
},
"d359777c-a124-4604-9062-b82f9462cf9d": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["15065f24-17eb-45af-b26f-95d0154da7a4"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p>I… Drank what? I had a… one of those… glasses, like ten minutes ago.</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["0438034d-adb8-4b21-8920-936d7814bb4e"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 24200.0,
"y": 22260.0
},
"d4cc204b-19c7-4289-ac50-1917bd32633e": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>Frank: …Sometimes, yeah. But I guess after enough exposure, you grow desensitized to the sight of-</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["b92e1b7a-cb86-45ab-933b-54112c3c4726"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 8460.0,
"y": 11520.0
},
"d560c822-c3d4-46e6-b8d8-a5e2bc72c028": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["661eaeaf-2163-48c1-8ed1-750cde420a56"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>End sequence where we hear sirens and see Vicky get carried away by EMS. Liv goes with her. </p><p>The sounds of the sirens cause partygoers to panic and scatter. After a bit, Frank stumbles out of the house, a little tipsy. You’re still sitting on the porch.</p><p></p>",
"height": 381.0,
"outputs": ["1fd7db8f-df1d-40f2-ac39-9f216a0318d0"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 29120.0,
"y": 19740.0
},
"d5af295e-8291-408b-b973-2ba41b683eeb": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>[Name]: Are you okay??</p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["c4847666-002b-4715-b18b-ed0f50964ae7"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 9640.0,
"y": 11140.0
},
"dd571a37-d393-4fd1-af4e-06158b4d9447": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["894c2a71-952e-45c9-b55a-340794307a1d"],
"content": "<p><strong>911-Operator:</strong> \"We’re sending a unit over right now. Please stay in place.</p>",
"height": 368.0,
"outputs": ["073c059a-4a19-4f34-ab06-931c46c4ce3c"],
"theme": "orange",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 11940.0,
"y": 13260.0
},
"ddc81088-660b-4114-aa9a-21996054bf4d": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["1f7c3344-557e-448c-b9a3-ccbaec7d4f2a"],
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345", "ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p><strong>Driver Friend:</strong> Bet you’re glad [Name] was there to save ya, huh?</p>",
"height": 326.0,
"outputs": ["44cbe662-6e56-43a6-b639-374973bf5136"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 21360.0,
"y": 20060.0
},
"de925341-5861-41e7-b508-897c401aa90c": {
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>They start spitting out the alcohol and vomiting on the floor.</p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["727a8512-257f-4a06-a91c-da35c5f31382"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 26600.0,
"y": 20800.0
},
"df1a4015-2832-414c-b9af-8563f42ff8da": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["09e64f42-693c-4f4f-9eca-b7930771ab6d"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p><em>You give the person the hot water.</em></p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["3ea72a9c-850a-45cc-8f4d-d9296ff8b7a2"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 25560.0,
"y": 20380.0
},
"e38ac378-7459-4c67-93c7-ba4be049631c": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["d0b52c34-c6a7-41b3-a108-10b74577e6b9"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><strong>Player:</strong> I’m not sure exactly, but it was more than 8 shots. I’m not sure how strong the alcohol is here.</p><p></p><p></p>",
"height": 364.0,
"outputs": ["a494cf80-b297-470e-a597-7e72b38ff410"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 27440.0,
"y": 19680.0
},
"e4531320-4418-404a-b9e9-d54afef0142c": {
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Now that they're feeling better, you decide to go check on the other person you saw.</p>",
"height": 140.0,
"outputs": ["3dcf3c6e-45fe-45b4-8504-6fd8cce06141"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 23900.0,
"y": 21140.0
},
"e5499f5b-b60b-4752-976a-9f257afef06a": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["771016cf-061a-4d82-9543-4045bf6bab7c"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p>Onlooker: In all my years of knowing them, I’ve never seen them drink even once.</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["f7e721c2-f9fd-4c91-b501-92f44b983615"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 25480.0,
"y": 18740.0
},
"e5f7f3ab-471b-42ad-b207-9b1e0035c10a": {
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p>I didn’t drink anything. I don’t trust these punch bowls anyway.</p>",
"height": 221.0,
"outputs": ["9d86d99d-8827-4af8-9ae9-3aa59cacc486"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 23600.0,
"y": 19060.0
},
"e67886eb-87cf-495f-bc93-44f536f20392": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["5b670f9d-477f-4f23-9874-68993ca808a2"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p>Onlooker: Oh god, Vicky! What the heck did you give her?</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["5affff52-68fe-4664-9de4-2ba96bb316d5"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 26960.0,
"y": 20660.0
},
"e8d059d1-ba3b-4732-a413-a0dc027ae038": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["2aeedc01-142b-4b03-af65-18005d83e752"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p>I…</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["66043d8a-8d4c-40e9-981a-d2c1051d2314"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 23540.0,
"y": 20080.0
},
"eab3ff1d-33b8-4e95-ab86-ffe2645abfac": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["9c479ff2-0ab8-4d64-94f8-47d89d366f57"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p><em>With shaky hands, they drink.</em></p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["9998a090-57e2-4eaa-81b3-15d0d3c13572"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 27580.0,
"y": 21240.0
},
"eb19b1f4-0cf1-48d7-b2f7-c4c219a3342e": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["7c2fadaa-8e4d-4870-aff0-c26aa90bbaca"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p>I pulled an all-nighter to finish it.</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["fd96a846-0e80-4465-b656-99f75e679317"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 24500.0,
"y": 19340.0
},
"ebed1e6d-b16a-4b3a-8ccf-8615e6103f1c": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["43f0c48e-4427-4037-915e-e9631ec1e56e"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p>What the heck is this? I already told you I don't drink.</p><p>I don't think I want your help anymore.</p>",
"height": 381.0,
"outputs": ["21b8f7d0-a632-48d9-9ecc-958b9a8ccef6"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 361.0,
"x": 24600.0,
"y": 20440.0
},
"ee290ed0-dd96-4d27-b019-089731e7bec2": {
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>You have to assess whether they are just sleep deprived, or actually suffering from alcohol poisoning.</em></p><p><em>Someone has just walked over.</em></p>",
"height": 176.0,
"outputs": ["92a6bb5f-5550-4be7-b024-d79577c483fd", "afd1784b-0f92-44d0-9dde-116c029d9274", "4772eb47-db04-462d-bfc9-c3cbb5c84fd8", "d406732e-dcc3-4dbc-90b1-17d98be33750", "f9a60e0c-735c-405e-b7c1-d2aa32ef3e09"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": "<p>Vicky</p>",
"width": 301.0,
"x": 25540.0,
"y": 21760.0
},
"ef7710b0-9aa7-4fd9-adfc-e96a4503b051": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["bd58b894-7f2a-4f84-94bf-94062057453e"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>Luckily, you’re outside, so you just have to look to the right, and the house number is there. Then, look to the left, to see the street sign.</em></p><p></p>",
"height": 361.0,
"outputs": ["8ca00d21-c3f6-4948-af4c-77ae0777cd79"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 27800.0,
"y": 20160.0
},
"ef796571-a5ea-42c4-8bfb-66e184da9e82": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["48b5e682-8d7e-4674-98a8-0fb8d833f185"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><strong>Liv: </strong>Okay, on their back. Now what?</p>",
"height": 261.0,
"outputs": ["acef5b38-f88d-4161-b5f5-fd4795a32c83"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 26540.0,
"y": 18540.0
},
"f0175fba-75a1-4cb2-8bc1-8551e68a70b8": {
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Well that could've gone better. You can't help a person who doesn't want help, though.</p><p>A little ways away at the party, you see someone fall to the ground and start giggling.</p><p>They look exhausted.</p>",
"height": 222.0,
"outputs": ["a0d128d0-1e03-454c-902d-7131d5b1b037"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 381.0,
"x": 23640.0,
"y": 20840.0
},
"f09dc359-b3f0-4671-a615-56f33d37f4bb": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["894c2a71-952e-45c9-b55a-340794307a1d"],
"content": "<p><strong>911-Operator:</strong> \"This is 911, what is your emergency?\"</p>",
"height": 421.0,
"outputs": ["4e64ef52-638a-4461-9646-7885d4309069"],
"theme": "orange",
"title": null,
"width": 281.0,
"x": 8860.0,
"y": 13060.0
},
"f1571a5e-abc0-4b4f-9302-46d2bb9f96f0": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["1b08e002-3aa2-4058-bb76-ce9e0a809bc7"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345", "647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p><strong>Frank: </strong>Usually that kind of injury means you lose the whole foot.</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["e714fcb4-50ac-407c-a622-c548f5141991"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 21160.0,
"y": 19640.0
},
"f2284647-5901-402f-9f18-96af7bcfb32e": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["2564654f-b745-4868-8444-639057403b6a"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p>Vicky: Hrrgh… I don’t wanna… Ugh… My head… hehe… Livvy..</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["88942ba9-0417-478a-b6a8-1832d8a1cb39"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 28560.0,
"y": 20720.0
},
"f252ac82-4648-4d41-89f4-04799795c0b5": {
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Based on your assessment, how will you help?</p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["b921ec36-add9-4f71-ac75-afc80d031dbe", "61c25322-a055-4d17-9ed9-fce5bb340ccb"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 26060.0,
"y": 21520.0
},
"f28349fa-f30e-40b2-8672-0426a7ee8ecd": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p><em>Suddenly, one of the knives falls down and impales your friend’s foot. You stand up with a jolt, knocking your water glass onto the ground.</em><br></p>",
"height": 321.0,
"outputs": ["5d41dc9d-4a64-43a6-96bc-7d422ccf13df"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 8560.0,
"y": 11900.0
},
"f46f5121-88de-4522-98dc-634636069fec": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p><strong>Frank</strong></p><p>Oh, hello there! Come on in! I was almost done making the food.</p>",
"height": 155.0,
"outputs": ["d6cc1b3c-3e70-42db-9a76-6de8a3fa613a"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 7140.0,
"y": 10940.0
},
"f4b48678-44bd-476d-965e-c6a6032f6b57": {
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>Your friends go to party in some side room, so you can’t find them. Cue the awkward moment when you’re at the party and you don’t actually know anyone. </em></p><p><br></p>",
"height": 161.0,
"outputs": ["c7b3d533-c867-45ac-a9dd-ad7ff72e0b75"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 22400.0,
"y": 20400.0
},
"f565f01d-d2d5-4745-a153-4a6c9029e07b": {
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>You have to assess whether they are just sleep deprived, or actually suffering from alcohol poisoning.</em></p><p><em>Someone has just walked over.</em></p>",
"height": 201.0,
"outputs": ["b9ec0f4c-920b-40d9-8a6b-655a43113e72", "eb8978af-9d16-4a07-aa42-b099647553a8", "4f3160b5-e616-4a14-b91c-4ad1aa328021", "e7a8db94-3ef2-4bf4-8a15-88aa5edfea8f", "776cf067-dde7-4c84-a905-66ffab40b530"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": "<p>Decoy</p>",
"width": 301.0,
"x": 25040.0,
"y": 19520.0
},
"f77d2647-faa5-4ec5-b9cd-a1040808f9e4": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>[Name]: I was just going to get some water to rinse the wound.</p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["074c70ca-ce13-43ff-89cc-6a55052de40c"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 11240.0,
"y": 10680.0
},
"f77e378b-0bcc-4387-9f13-7d20e483e596": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p>Frank: What are you doing?</p>",
"height": 301.0,
"outputs": ["133b7bcb-b8b3-423f-9fd1-d05a59adff6b"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 10780.0,
"y": 10660.0
},
"f7cb21fb-d8e8-449e-8772-a1679440ec94": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["647349ca-9ebb-4d5f-b81e-500761ec1c5a"],
"content": "<p><em>You look closer at the wound. Perhaps there was something in that medical bag that can help here?</em></p>",
"height": 140.0,
"outputs": ["5d15615c-a3e1-4c92-8744-cecb335092e7", "175bdb53-d25d-46d6-b812-efd70e3dd713"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 12200.0,
"y": 11000.0
},
"f8791b7e-3c53-418f-9c6f-777ae4d65a5e": {
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>Vicky vomits and passes out, collapsing on the floor. Liv catches them.</em></p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["f5d71f10-c7f0-4f8d-a036-65b81b244a41"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 29360.0,
"y": 20980.0
},
"f8fa5ace-c61b-4b8d-9f00-d5d85e54f488": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["40e77927-dbe4-4dd9-ac39-404a90cf3aa2"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345", "1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p><em>Suddenly, you see two people who appear very exhausted. They both appear to have trouble walking. You don't know who they are.</em></p><p><em>Who do you help?</em></p><p></p>",
"height": 381.0,
"outputs": ["d2fc59ec-c723-4d0b-a7aa-371e30422254", "a3b3ebce-498b-48c5-bbf8-47ce6a4d928d"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 22820.0,
"y": 19900.0
},
"fa52f960-9711-4abf-8101-d1fe0592c7df": {
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em> Liv is holding Vicky steady on her side.</em></p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["725f1f4e-2af2-4adb-960f-4a7020af7973"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 28940.0,
"y": 19340.0
},
"fabf46c1-a7ff-4460-84f4-ec89e33087e8": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["edef6177-1574-4d01-9862-4251f6276aad"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><strong>Player:</strong> I already checked. I have her friend giving CPR right now.</p><p></p>",
"height": 364.0,
"outputs": ["27c6c433-a0de-4114-b010-301c2a2c121f"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 26740.0,
"y": 19680.0
},
"fac99888-f592-465d-9b89-b40d5656b804": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["06f6a2f0-b8bc-4983-9db6-d05452b79bf7"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><strong>Player: </strong>I’m putting her on her side so she doesn’t choke on her vomit.</p>",
"height": 241.0,
"outputs": ["06d49c33-4a4f-4140-90d3-fd7a776afa15"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 29960.0,
"y": 19380.0
},
"fadf0695-a237-4b38-9a6b-f54ade8bdc0f": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"attributes": ["d8c4252b-6c52-4b6f-aefb-8b819740cc31"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["1f4389b8-e21a-4d12-84c7-c36cc0c50345"],
"content": "<p><em>You give the person the hot tea.</em></p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["8429bcd9-be6f-4d0a-a1ec-2f8da3b6988a"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 26900.0,
"y": 21720.0
},
"fd09b426-c4be-44bd-ac0c-8c2804c3ab70": {
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>It’s a hot night out tonight.</em></p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["b9da7664-7fbf-4b0a-aa2f-888464993e99"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 28960.0,
"y": 20820.0
},
"fead337b-50f4-4ba1-a8c5-41af245adaab": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "7202d1ea-e81d-4292-8cd3-bd9cf6d5b1bd",
"type": "image"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["ad3d9699-c9ea-4bc0-aa9f-e9656ca0791c"],
"content": "<p>Frank:You think some of these situations are unbelievable, but then they always show pictures in the slides from real events.</p>",
"height": 301.0,
"outputs": ["19c6b2f2-82a4-48e1-be47-3dfd1e57a0ba"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 321.0,
"x": 8220.0,
"y": 12400.0
}
},
"jumpers": {
